This study is aimed to comprehensively establish the bio-similarity/bioequivalence in EPIAO(R) and EPREX(R) in terms of 52-week comparisons in efficacy, safety and immunogenicity.

 The targeted population is anaemia patients with end-stage chronic renal disease who previously received epoetin treatment and on haemodialysis.

